《核心危机》日本发售首日售出35万份，其中包括77,777套限量版PSP/《核心危机》同捆包<ref>{{cite web| date=2007-09-16| title=FFVII: Crisis Core sells 350,000 copies on first day| url=http://www.gamegrep.com/news/5237-ffvii_crisis_core_sells_350000_copies_on_first_day/| publisher=Gamegrep.com| accessdate=2007-09-16| archive-date=2007-10-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016055935/http://www.gamegrep.com/news/5237-ffvii_crisis_core_sells_350000_copies_on_first_day/| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。史克威尔艾尼克斯在2007年11月宣布，核心危机是他们5月到9月间全球范围最畅销的游戏，其中日本售出71万<ref>{{cite web | author=Powell, Chris | date=2007-11-22 | title=Crisis Core is Square's best selling game this year | url=http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/21/crisis-core-is-squares-best-selling-game-this-year/ | publisher=MaxConsole.net | accessdate=2007-11-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128170407/http://www.joystiq.com/2007/11/21/crisis-core-is-squares-best-selling-game-this-year/ | archive-date=2015-01-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2008年3月，《核心危机》在美国首月售出30.16万套<ref name="NPDmarch">{{cite web | author=Sinclair, Brendan | date=2008-04-17 | title=NPD: March game sales skyrocket 57 percent | url=http://www.gamespot.com//news/npd-march-game-sales-skyrocket-57-percent-6189483? | publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | accessdate=2008-05-22 | archive-date=2013-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622225736/http://www.gamespot.com/news/npd-march-game-sales-skyrocket-57-percent-6189483 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，以仅次于《[[战神：奥林匹斯之链|战神：奥林匹斯之链]]》34.05万的销量成为三月第二畅销PlayStation Portable游戏，并成为全平台第6畅销游戏<ref name="NPDmarch" />。史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布，到2009年3月31日时《核心危机》全球售出310万套，其中日本83万<ref>{{cite web | title=Results Briefing: Fiscal Year ended May 31, 2009 | date=2009-05-19 | url=http://www.hd.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090525_01en.pdf#8 | work=Square-Enix.com | accessdate=2009-07-21 | archive-date=2015-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912080046/http://www.hd.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090525_01en.pdf#8 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在史克威尔艾尼克斯2009财年售出84万，其中欧洲55万<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.siliconera.com/2009/05/21/what-square-enix-games-sold-well-last-year/ | title = What Square Enix Games Sold Well Last Year? | publisher = Siliconera | author = Spenser | date = 2009-05-21 | accessdate = 2009-05-21 | archive-date = 2009-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090523092822/http://www.siliconera.com/2009/05/21/what-square-enix-games-sold-well-last-year/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。作为对游戏销量的回应，史克威尔艾尼克斯授予《核心危机》他们当年最佳PSP游戏称号<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/crisis-core-biggest-psp-release-of-2008 | title = Crisis Core 'biggest PSP release of 2008' | publisher = [[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]] | author = Ingh".am, Tim | date = 2008-06-13 | accessdate = 2010-08-25 | archive-date = 2011-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110714064634/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/crisis-core-biggest-psp-release-of-2008 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，称其为“不可思议的成功”。史克威尔英国销售总监道格·博恩称其为“2008年必备PSP游戏”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/square-enixs-crisis-core-reigns-supreme-over-psp-chart | title = Square Enix's Crisis Core reigns supreme over PSP chart | publisher = [[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]] | author = Harker, Jonathon | date = 2008-08-29 | accessdate = 2010-08-25 | archive-date = 2011-07-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110714064705/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/square-enixs-crisis-core-reigns-supreme-over-psp-chart | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《核心危机》普遍获得积极评价。游戏在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的评论综合得分为82%<ref name="gr" />，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的得分为83<ref name="meta" />。日本游戏杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》上的游戏总分为35/40，四个独立评分为9/9/8/9<ref name="maxconsole2007" />。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]授予游戏“编辑推荐”称号，称赞其故事、战斗系统及其呈现，并称“《核心危机》是一次激动且令人沉痛的旅行，所有角色扮演游戏爱好者都应该展开这旅程”<ref name="gspot" />。[[IGN|IGN]]的莱安·克莱门茨因游戏聚焦于札克斯的成长及他同战士们的友情，而称赞游戏有别于其他角色扮演游戏。他称“《核心危机》是一款很棒的游戏，除了各处的一些小问题，它不会令人失望”。游戏还进入PlayStation Portable平台推荐游戏的“编辑精选”栏<ref name="ignreview" />。[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]也给游戏好评，称其“胜任致敬部分，并将传统设计的精华和全新的技术独到结合，协调汇集了将一些旧物和一些新品”。GameSpy也称一些玩家可能不喜欢札克斯，“你将对角色不跟着你的冒险成长而相当厌倦”<ref name="Gspy" />。
[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]给了游戏9分的总评，认为其战斗系统“使人上瘾”，并提出CGI场景动画和《最终幻想VII -降临之子-》的质量相似<ref name="videogamereview" />。《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》也给游戏相似的积极评价，称其为“视效最好的PSP作品”，并称赞其同补完计划的元素结成一体，并同时创造了新方面<ref name="gamepro" />。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的AJ·格拉瑟称有了DMW系统，游戏将会简单，让“半熟玩家”也尝试以困难模式玩游戏。格拉瑟还认为游戏足够讨人喜爱，甚至让不喜欢最终幻想VII系列的玩家也开始喜欢它<ref name="gradar" />。《[[Play_(英国杂志)|Play]]》的塞缪尔·罗伯茨称游戏为2008年最佳游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.play-mag.co.uk/opinion/crisis-core-final-fantasy-vii-%e2%80%93-my-game-of-the-year/|title=Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII – my game of the year|work=[[Play_(UK_magazine)|Play]]|accessdate=2010-09-11|author=Roberts, Samuel|archive-date=2011-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719014615/http://www.play-mag.co.uk/opinion/crisis-core-final-fantasy-vii-%E2%80%93-my-game-of-the-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

许多评论还提到了游戏和《最终幻想VII》的关系。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]称其为史上最佳前传之一，提出游戏“更好的将玩家放入《FFVII》的世界，甚至超越了原作所为”<ref name="oneupreview" />。而[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]称《核心危机》“并非省事与复制资源”，他们认为游戏和《地狱犬的挽歌》不同，更能吸引玩家<ref name="Gt" />。《[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]》称虽然游戏主线情节只有12小时，但支线任务帮游戏加长了时间。他们还称赞战斗系统“永不无聊”，同时《最终幻想VII》漫长游荡和过长中心的缺点在本作不是问题<ref name="cvg" />。

然而游戏获得一些负面评价。虽然[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]称其为最佳《最终幻想VII》衍生作品，但也批评称“对于其针对的26、28、30岁者，游戏除了完美的伤感外，鲜有演出其它内容”<ref name="eurogamereview" />。虽然[[PALGN|PALGN]]将DWM系统称为“简便的工具”，但同时认为这是游戏的最大弱点<ref name="palgn" />。[[X-Play|X-Play]]给游戏打出2/5，对无法跳过的过场、欠佳的对话、反复的游戏性以及薄弱的剧情表示不满<ref name="xplay">{{cite web | author=D.F. Smith | date=2008-03-25 | title=X-Play reviews Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII | url=http://www.g4tv.com/games/psp/27927/crisis-core-final-fantasy-vii/ | publisher=[[G4tv.com|G4tv.com]] | accessdate=2008-03-25 | archive-date=2012-10-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016202020/http://www.g4tv.com/games/psp/27927/crisis-core-final-fantasy-vii/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[愚人节|愚人节]]他们对其原始评论的回应称，他们“决定再看一遍游戏，并重新为其评论，这次给予游戏完全公正的观点”，他们讽刺的给原版配音并打出了不可能高的6/5<ref>{{cite web | date=2008-04-01 | archivedate=2008年7月4日 | title=X-Play rereviews Crisis Core: Final Fantasy VII | url=http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/features/21036/Crisis_Core_Final_Fantasy_VII_ReReview.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704140808/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/features/21036/Crisis_Core_Final_Fantasy_VII_ReReview.html | publisher=[[G4tv.com|G4tv.com]] | accessdate=2008-04-01 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

《核心危机》获得多家媒体的数项奖项。游戏获得GameSpot“2008年最佳”将的“最佳情节”“最佳RPG游戏”和“最佳PSP游戏”提名，并赢得“最佳PSP游戏”奖。游戏还列入IGN史上最佳PSP游戏第十名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/12/28/the-top-25-psp-games?page=4|page=4|title=The Top 25 PSP Games of All Time|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2010-07-23|archive-date=2012-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120901220240/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/12/28/the-top-25-psp-games?page=4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在IGN“2008年十大PSP剧情”中有4篇关于本游戏的文章，其中位于首位的是游戏评论文章<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/01/07/the-top-10-psp-stories-of-2008|date=2009-01-07|title=The Top 10 PSP Stories of 2008|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2010-07-24|archive-date=2012-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102065437/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/01/07/the-top-10-psp-stories-of-2008|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在IGN 2008年最佳游戏中，《核心危机》获得“最佳RPG”和“最佳PSP情节”将<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/psp/5.html|title=IGN PSP: Best RPG 2008|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2010-07-25|archive-date=2012-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311042149/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/psp/5.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestof.ign.com/2008/psp/13.html|title=IGN PSP: Best Story 2008|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2010-07-25|archive-date=2012-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311042156/http://bestof.ign.com/2008/psp/13.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。游戏获得Videogamer.com“2008年最佳游戏”第15位及“2008年十大PlayStation独占游戏”第4位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/features/article/24-12-208-590-3.html|title=Best Games of 2008|date=2008-12-24|publisher=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|accessdate=2010-08-26}}{{dead link|date=June 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps3/metal_gear_solid_4/features/article/top_10_playstation_exclusives_of_2008.html|title=Top 10 PlayStation exclusives of 2008|date=2008-12-27|publisher=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|accessdate=2010-08-26|archive-date=2012-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927065524/http://www.videogamer.com/ps3/metal_gear_solid_4/features/article/top_10_playstation_exclusives_of_2008.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《GamePro》将游戏列为五款PSP玩家应玩游戏之一，2009年31款最佳PSP游戏之一，以及最佳电子游戏前传第7名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/214542/five-games-you-should-play-on-psp-before-the-consoles-lifecycle-ends/|title=Five games you should play on PSP before the console's lifecycle ends|date=2010-03-24|author=Glasser, AJ; Rudden, Dave|publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|accessdate=2010-09-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100812090115/http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/214542/five-games-you-should-play-on-psp-before-the-consoles-lifecycle-ends/|archivedate=2010-08-12|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/211288/the-31-best-psp-games-page-2-of-4/|author=Erickson, Trick|title=The 31 Best PSP Games - 2009 Edition|date=2009-07-16|publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|accessdate=2010-09-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100809202154/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/211288/the-31-best-psp-games-page-2-of-4/|archivedate=2010-08-09|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209646/game-prequels-the-8-greatest-video-game-prequels/|author=Noble, McKinley; Shaw, Patrick|title=Game Prequels: The 8 Greatest Video Game Prequels|date=2009-04-07|publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|accessdate=2010-09-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024035648/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/209646/game-prequels-the-8-greatest-video-game-prequels/|archivedate=2010-10-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。游戏还在《[[电击_(杂志)|电击]]》史上最令人流泪游戏票选中获得第3名<ref>{{cite web|title=【アンケート結果発表】感動して泣いてしまったゲームはありますか?|url=http://news.dengeki.com/elem/000/000/113/113442/|publisher=[[ASCII_Media_Works|ASCII Media Works]]|date=2008-10-15|accessdate=2012-05-07|language=ja|archive-date=2012-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419012624/http://news.dengeki.com/elem/000/000/113/113442/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏在2011年获得《Fami通》同主题读者投票的第2位<ref>{{cite web|last=Romano|first=Sal|url=http://gematsu.com/2011/12/famitsus-top-20-list-of-tear-inducing-games|title=Famitsu's top 20 list of tear-inducing games|date=2011-12-29|accessdate=2012-02-24|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306155226/http://gematsu.com/2011/12/famitsus-top-20-list-of-tear-inducing-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

